snippet.textDisplay:
1st impressions: Interesting experiment. Taking on a legendary classic. Change of composition, fusion with new instruments and addition of Qawwali component. Good attempt 
After 10th view: This is unique in many ways. Not a run of the mill song
After 100th View: This is much deeper than I thought
After 200th view: Wow
After 500th view: I cant stop listening
After 1000th View: Ok, I admit its genuinely mystic, well thought out  and inspired work. Its boring into me every time I listen to it.
